      </div>
      <div class="left-object caption">
        <p><span class="strong">売上</span>集計</p>
      </div>
      <div class="left-object caption">
        <p><span class="strong">整理券</span>連動</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vertical-text right-object phrase">
        <p>仕事よ舞え。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview">
